snippet.title: Alex's Caves Announcement
snippet.description:
Music used in video: https://youtu.be/XQ2QyFrqy8g

Yep, you heard it here first! Alex's Caves will be published to Curseforge on October 19th, 2023 - A exact year after development first began! Prepare to enter five new, rare cave biomes in Minecraft Forge 1.20.1. Which will you be heading to first?

-Discord: https://discord.gg/alexsmods
-Twitter: https://twitter.com/AlexModGuy
(Disclaimer: Although we hope to upload the mod on the 19th, there is no guarantee it well appear for everyone at the same time. This is a general ballpark date that after which the mod should be downloadable.)
